### API Gateway Test File

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health

### User Service Routes (through gateway)
### Register user (public)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "password123",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "fullName": "Test User"
}

### Login user (public)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get current user (requires JWT)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Order Service Routes (through gateway, requires JWT)
### Create order (requires JWT)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "productCode": "PROD-001",
      "productName": "Laptop",
      "quantity": 1,
      "price": 999.99
    }
  ]
}

### Get order by ID (requires JWT)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Inventory Service Routes (through gateway, requires JWT)
### Get all inventory
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inventory
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Payment Service Routes (through gateway, requires JWT)
### Get payment by order ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/payments/order/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Shipping Service Routes (through gateway, requires JWT)
### Get shipment by order ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/shipping/order/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Gateway Routes
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/gateway/routes
